PrecisReappointment of DAVID M. SCOTT of Saskatoon, Saskatchewan, and JOHN LINDSAY, Q.C., of Edmonton, Alberta, to be part-time members of the National Parole Board, Prairies Regional Division, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of three years, effective May 27, 2006.
